<opener><lb/>Viro Illustrissimo et Clarissimo <rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person">Petro Antonio Michelotti</rs>
<lb/><abbr>S. P. D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nicolaus Bernoulli</rs>.</opener>
<p><lb/>Siquidem officii meii ratio postulet, ut Tibi quam citissime
         <lb/>post meum in <rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Urbem</rs> hanc adventum gratias agam pro beneficiis
         <lb/>et honoribus, quibus me in <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dibus Tuis mactare Tibi placuit, ut
         <lb/>et pro laboribus, quos negotiis meis curandis tam benevole impendere
         <lb/>voluisti; nolui deesse officio meo, quapropter has ad Te exaro
         <lb/>literas, ut de grato meo in Te animo Tibi constet, quem data occa<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>sione nunquam non evidentius declarare studebo. Diem quo pri<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mam Lectionem facturus sum, adhucdum ignoro, ultra duas hebdo<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>madas impendere opus habeo audiendis Lectionibus reliquorum Pro<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>fessorum, ita ut nonnisi post tres hebdomadas munus meum me
         <lb/>aggressurum sperem. Nunc non aliud Tibi significandum habeo, quam
         <lb/>me <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> <abbr>D.</abbr> Marchione <rs key="pers_DE-588-11887733X" type="person">Poleni</rs> amicissime receptum esse, et adhucdum
         <lb/>nullo non beneficii genere affici. Spero cistam meam ad D. <rs type="person">Westen<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>apel</rs><!-- persontag EK: Westenapel konnte nicht identifiziert werden--> brevi perventuram esse, eam si quam cito fieri poterit huc
         <lb/>mitti curabis, rem gratissimam mihi praestabis. Beneficio etiam me
         <lb/>afficies, si Patronis, qui mihi bene cupiunt, obsequii meii cultus de<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>feres. <abbr>Ill.</abbr> <abbr>D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-11887733X" type="person">Poleni</rs> meis verbis salutem plurimam Tibi ascribit.</p>
<lb/><closer><salute>Vale et mihi porro fave.</salute> <dateline><rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavii</rs> <date when="1716-11-24">Octavo <abbr>Cal.</abbr> <abbr>Dec.</abbr> MDCCXVI.</date></dateline></closer>
</div></body></text></TEI>